headline: Ahead of Best Buy (BBY) Q3 Earnings: Get Ready With Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for Best Buy (BBY), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended October 2024.
